items.desc: Here in The Goddess Girls Wiki, you can learn more about the book series written by Joan Holub and Suzanne Williams. Contribute to add information on this wiki. You could see book summaries, character information and many more! Be sure to read the character information to know more about your favorite Goddess Girls characters.
